Hi Alex, can you check this one out?
Anthony, can you attach the diagram for which you get this error?

I just created a new geoshape diagram.

I do not seem to get this exception on any other diagram.

This happens when the diagram view doesn't have a reference to semantic element and there is no parser contributed. In this case the name to display is grabbed from Description style. TreeEditPart casts Description style to ShapeStyle which is not the case for the TreeDiagramEditPart. In fact, the cast to ShapeStyle is absolutely unnecessary, since we only asking the style for description which is a member of DescriptionStyle. Therefore, the fix will be don't cast DescrptionStyle to ShapeStyle - just work with DescriptionStyle
Fix committed for 2.0.1 to R2_maintenance and HEAD streams
